  "slug": "vibrant-parrots",
  "title": "Vibrant Parrots",
  "description": "New colorful parrots, breeding, eggs, and portable cages for the ultimate bird companion.",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/vibrantparrots/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/vibrantparrots/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"https://lunapixel.studio/discord\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Discord&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"117\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://x.com/Fusseel\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Twitter&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=x&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"116\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@heyitsfuzs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=YouTube&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=youtube&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"118\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Fuzss\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=GitHub&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"108\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/fuzs_\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=CurseForge&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"143\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Fuzs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Modrinth&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"129\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/vibrantparrots/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/about.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Vibrant Parrots</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> expands Minecraft's parrots with new colors, breeding, eggs, and bird cages, giving these jungle companions a much richer pet experience. 🦜</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Discover 11 additional parrot variants for a total of 16 colorful birds to find, collect, and breed. Parrots can now lay eggs that hatch into chicks, making it possible to build and grow your own flock. 🐣</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The mod also makes parrots easier to travel with. Carry tamed birds in portable cages, and customize shoulder sitting behavior to take your cute companions wherever your adventures lead. 🎒</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Parrot variants finally become fully data-driven and can be extended using data packs with custom textures, allowing entirely new colors and species to be added. 🎨</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/vibrantparrots/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/features.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🦜 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">16 Colorful Parrots:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Discover 11 additional parrot variants beyond Minecraft's original five.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🌿 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Natural Spawning:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> New variants appear naturally in jungles alongside vanilla parrots.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🐣 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Parrot Breeding &amp; Eggs:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Breed parrots, collect eggs, and hatch them into adorable chicks.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">📦 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Bird Cages:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Carry tamed parrots in portable cages for easy transport and relocation.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🪶 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">New Shoulder Behavior:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Configure when parrots stay on or leave your shoulders.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⚙️ </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Configurable Gameplay:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Adjust egg laying and shoulder behavior to suit your preferred experience.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🎨 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Data-Driven Variants:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Add your own parrot variants using data packs and custom textures.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/vibrantparrots/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/media.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/vibrantparrots/media/1.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/vibrantparrots/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/installation.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">INSTALLATION REQUIRED ON CLIENT &amp; REQUIRED ON SERVER</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/puzzles-lib\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PUZZLES LIB</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC &amp; NEOFORGE)</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FABRIC API</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC)</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/forge-config-api-port\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FORGE CONFIG API PORT</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC)</span></strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/vibrantparrots/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/configuration.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">If available for a mod, configuration is possible directly from in-game using the mod menu (requires </span><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/modmenu\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Mod Menu</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> by </span><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Prospector\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Prospector</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> to be installed on Fabric).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">For manual configuration using an external text editor all files are found at </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">.minecraft/config</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, named as </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-client.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-common.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, or </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-server.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, depending on the type of config. Not all types might exist for a mod, if any at all.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/vibrantparrots/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/credits.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🌟 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Huge thanks to </span><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/sixfootblue\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">SixFootBlue</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> for the original </span><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/transmobifier-16x\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">TransMobifier</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> resource pack, whose colorful parrot variants served as the foundation for this mod.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🌟 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Thanks to </span><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/vazkii\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Vazkii</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> for creating </span><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/quark\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Quark</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, which inspired the parrot breeding and egg mechanics in this mod.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🌟 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Thanks to </span><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/MisterHyacinth\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MisterHyacinth</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> for creating </span><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/psittacine\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Psittacine</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, which inspired the bird cage feature in this mod.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🌟 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Special thanks to </span><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/l200\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">L200</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> for creating the item textures used throughout this mod, including the bird cage and colored parrot eggs.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/vibrantparrots/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/visual-workbench\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/visualworkbench/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/overflowing-bars\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/overflowingbars/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/illager-invasion\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/illagerinvasion/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/vibrantparrots/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://lunapixel.studio/discord\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/studio.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/vibrantparrots/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n",
